12. ğŸ‘‡ï¸ set configure in settings.py for media, static, templates, App_Login, App_Shop, App_Order, App_Payment

13. ğŸ‘‡ï¸ create urls.py in application (App_Login, App_Shop, App_Order, App_Payment) and make connection between main urls.py with application urls.py 

14. ğŸ‘‡ï¸ create views.py in main project

14. ğŸ‘‡ï¸ start developing project from login (Step-1: 7.1.1,  Step-2: 7.1.2)
